# Implementation Plan: Adepu Pranav's Premium Portfolio Website

This document outlines the technical implementation plan to transform the existing portfolio into a premium, modern, dark minimalistic, futuristic single-page application for Adepu Pranav, showcasing AI, Backend, Cloud, Networking, ML, and Unity skills.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - The entire existing content (currently tailored to G. Pranay Sai) will be replaced with Adepu Pranav's details.
> - The design will shift to a deep navy/black gradient theme with Electric Blue, Violet Glow, and Cyan accents.
> - I will use a glowing profile placeholder image for the hero section as requested.
> - Please review the proposed changes below and approve them before I proceed with the execution.

## Proposed Changes

### Design System (CSS)
- **Colors**: Deep navy to black background (`#0A0A0A` to `#020617`), Accents: Electric Blue (`#3B82F6`), Violet Glow (`#8B5CF6`), Cyan (`#06B6D4`).
- **Typography**: Headings: 'Sora' (or 'Poppins' if Sora is unavailable), Body: 'Inter'.
- **Effects**: Glassmorphism (`backdrop-filter: blur()`), Neon glows (`box-shadow`), floating animations, fade-ins.
- **Layout**: CSS Grid/Flexbox for fully responsive design.

---

### File Modifications

#### [MODIFY] index.html
- **Header/Nav**: Update title to "Adepu Pranav | Portfolio". Create a sticky navbar with smooth scroll links to new sections. Add scroll progress indicator.
- **Hero Section**: 
  - Add Adepu Pranav's name, short intro, and dynamic typing effect for the roles.
  - Add Buttons (View Projects, Contact Me, Download Resume).
  - Add glowing profile placeholder.
- **About Section**: Split-layout glass cards with the provided bio and details.
- **Skills Section**: Grouped animated skill bars/cards (Programming, Backend/Cloud, Networking, AI/ML, Game Dev, Tools).
- **Projects Section**: Interactive cards with hover glow, tags, and links for the 7 specified projects.
- **Experience Section**: Animated timeline for the IRISET Intern role.
- **Achievements Section**: Glowing cards for the 3 hackathon achievements.
- **Leadership Section**: Modern cards for COO and VP roles.
- **Education Section**: Animated timeline for Geethanjali College.
- **Interests Section**: Interactive icon-based cards.
- **Contact Section**: Glassmorphism form, social links, floating labels.

#### [MODIFY] style.css
- Define CSS variables for the new color palette.
- Implement glassmorphism utility classes (`.glass-card`).
- Add glowing accent classes (`.glow-blue`, `.glow-violet`, `.glow-cyan`).
- Implement floating gradient blobs using pseudo-elements or absolute positioning.
- Add keyframe animations for floating elements, fade-in transitions, and hover states.
- Style the scroll progress indicator.
- Apply modern, clean spacing and layouts for all the new sections.

#### [MODIFY] script.js
- Implement the animated typing effect for the hero section roles using JavaScript.
- Enhance the intersection observer for scroll reveal transitions (fade-in, slide-up).
- Update the scroll progress indicator logic.
- Update active section highlighting logic in the navbar based on the new sections.
- Add event listeners for the new contact form (prevent default submission and show a success animation).

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated/Local Testing
- Open `index.html` in the local browser to verify:
  - The dark futuristic theme and colors are applied correctly.
  - The typing animation in the Hero section rotates correctly through the roles.
  - All sections are present and populated with the correct data.
  - Glassmorphism and glow effects render as expected.
  - Responsive behavior on mobile, tablet, and desktop views.

### Manual Verification
- The user will view the `index.html` in their browser.
- The user will verify smooth scrolling and active navbar link highlighting.
- The user will check the interactive hover effects on projects and skills.
